titleStmt.title: Decrees and orders of the Committee of Safcty [sic] of the Commonwealth of Oceana.

notesStmt.note: On t.p.: "Ordered that these decrees be forthwith printed and published. John Harrington, Clerk to the Committee."
Reproductions of originals in the Henry E. Huntington Library and Art Gallery (Early English books) and the British Library (Thomason Tracts).
